					<div class="card-body">
						<code>OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key <br></code>
						<code>CONNECTION_STRING_MONGODB=you_monogodb_connection_string_here</code>
					</div>
				</div>

				<h3 id="api-integration" class="mt-5">API Integration</h3>
				<h4 id="openai-api-integration" class="mt-3">OpenAI API Integration</h4>
				<p>Integrate OpenAI's API to analyze the content of uploaded resumes and generate career path
					recommendations. Ensure proper configuration and handling of API requests to maintain performance
					and reliability. The following steps are required to ensure OpenAIâ€™s API integration is successfully
